29
00:01:54,367 --> 00:01:55,535
Terima kasih.

30
00:01:57,746 --> 00:01:59,539
Kau menyelamatkanku.

31
00:01:59,623 --> 00:02:01,625
Kerja bagus, Nak!

32
00:02:02,375 --> 00:02:03,376
Jangan bergerak!

33
00:02:04,419 --> 00:02:05,420
Letakkan senjatamu!

34
